      <title>美国将继续对俄罗斯液化天然气供应“施压”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/us-will-continue-to-tighten-the-screws-on-russian-lng-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院一位高级能源官员称，美国将继续“加大对俄罗斯液化天然气出口的限制”，以切断莫斯科用于乌克兰战争的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/us-will-continue-to-tighten-the-screws-on-russian-lng-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 04:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
